arts.ttl: Barrow v Cheltenham Town RECAP: Robins sunk by second-half Bluebirds fightback after Ryan Bowman opener
arts.sum: Cheltenham Town allowed a lead to slip away in the second half as they went down 2-1 at Barrow on Saturday afternoon. But Emile Acquah levelled two minutes into the second half and substitute Andy Dallas won it for the Bluebirds in the 86th minute.

arts.ttl: Barrow snatch late winner against Cheltenham
arts.sum: Andrew Dallas stepped off the bench to cap a comeback win.
